on the Cauldron of the Cosmos?

191
00:14:37,640 --> 00:14:39,274
Is that what it is?

192
00:14:42,044 --> 00:14:43,979
I'm going to allow that.

193
00:14:46,148 --> 00:14:47,581
If Thanos needs all six,
why don't we just

194
00:14:47,583 --> 00:14:49,215
