259
00:18:34,575 --> 00:18:36,408
- What's going on?
- Oh, my God!

260
00:18:44,786 --> 00:18:46,117
What's the matter
with you kids?

261
00:18:46,119 --> 00:18:47,755
You never seen
a spaceship before?

262
